highlights.text: “用背脊唱情歌” by Gareth.T has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 100 days straight.
CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “GO!” is the highest at #2.
“Wake Me up When September Ends” by Green Day is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 52 spots at #14.
“By Chance, By Fate” by Kim Youngwoo is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #75.
